#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/opentelemetry.adoc:570
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"TracingMetadata tm = TracingMetadata.withPrevious(Context.current());\n"
"Message out = Message.of(...).withMetadata(tm);\n"
